net.morimekta.providence.config

Class MessageBuilderConfig<Message extends PMessage<Message,Field>,Field extends PField>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.morimekta.providence.config.MessageBuilderConfig<Message,Field>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.morimekta.config.Config, net.morimekta.config.ConfigBuilder<MessageBuilderConfig<Message,Field>>, ProvidenceConfig, ProvidenceConfigBuilder<MessageBuilderConfig<Message,Field>>

    public class MessageBuilderConfig<Message extends PMessage<Message,Field>,Field extends PField>
extends Object
implements ProvidenceConfigBuilder<MessageBuilderConfig<Message,Field>>
    A config that wraps a providence message builder instance. Because the content may change during the lifetime, using this config as a lookup mechanism is not recommended.

    Note that the message builder config is NOT thread safe at all.
